	* ftpd/pam.c (pam_user): Likewise.
	* ifconfig/if_index.c (if_freenameindex): Likewise.
	* inetd/inetd.c (freeconfig, getconfigent): Likewise.
	* libinetutils/argcv.c (int argcv_free): Likewise.
