	* tftp/Makefile.am (INCLUDES): Add libinetutils
	* tftp/main.c: Fixed possible memory overruns.
	(setpeer): Fixed coredump on hitting return after '(to)' prompt.
	Fixed indentation.
	* tftp/tftp.c: Fixed indentation.

